# **REST API Documentation**
## **Get /event**
This endpoint is to list all event available inside of the DB.
<br>

### **Response Status**
```
Success
=======
200 OK

Error
=======
500 internal server error
```

### **Response Body**
```
Successful sample:
====================
[ 
   dataEvent:
    {
        "id": integer,
        "title": "string",
        "content": "string",
        "eventDate": "date",
        "UserId": integer,
        "imageUrl": "string",
        "createdAt": "date",
        "updatedAt": "date"
    },
```
    ]
<br>
#### **POST /register**
This endpoint is to register user
<br>

### **Response Status**
```
Success
=======
201 OK

Error
=======
500 internal server error
```
### **Response Body**
```
Successful sample:
====================
{
    "id": integer,
    "email": "String"
}
```
<br>

## **POST /login**
This endpoint is to list all Posts available inside of the DB.
<br>

### **Response Status**
```
Success
=======
200 OK

Error
=======
500 something happend with plis try again later
```

### **Response Body**
```
Successful sample:
====================
{
    access_token:'string'
}
```
<br>

